headline: Centuri Holdings (CTRI) Q4 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: Centuri (CTRI) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -12.82% and +19.67%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
